title: Screaming at higher pitch than nicktron: Spoiled Tea over my 200 Euro Corsair K70 RGB Keyboard
body:
Hey guys,

I played ranked while having a cold and had a cup of tea right in front of me between me and my Keyboard. Of Course it had to happened that I knocked over the Cup and spoiled all the tea over my Keyboard while live on stream. I was Streaming at a higher pitch than nicktron and my teammate could not stop laughing on voice.
